Class ReferralRequest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class ReferralRequest
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR ReferralRequest Resource (A request for referral or tranfer of care)

    Definition: Used to record and send details about a request for referral service or transfer of a patient to the care of another provider or provider organisation

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/ReferralRequest
